n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Limits/Shapes/Pullback/IsPullback/Defs.html#CategoryTheory.IsPushout\">IsPushout</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.CategoryStruct.comp\">CategoryStruct.comp</a> <span class=\"fn\">h₁₁</span> <span class=\"fn\">h₁₂</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">v₁₁</span> <span class=\"fn\">v₁₃</span> <span class=\"fn\">h₂₃</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">t</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Limits/Shapes/Pullback/IsPullback/Defs.html#CategoryTheory.IsPushout\">IsPushout</a> <span class=\"fn\">h₁₁</span> <span class=\"fn\">v₁₁</span> <span class=\"fn\">v₁₂</span> <span class=\"fn\">h₂₁</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Limits/Shapes/Pullback/IsPullback/Defs.html#CategoryTheory.IsPushout\">IsPushout</a> <span class=\"fn\">h₁₂</span> <span class=\"fn\">v₁₂</span> <span class=\"fn\">v₁₃</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">t</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Limits/Shapes/Pullback/IsPullback/Defs.html#CategoryTheory.IsPushout.desc\">desc</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.CategoryStruct.comp\">CategoryStruct.comp</a> <span class=\"fn\">h₁₂</span> <span class=\"fn\">v₁₃</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">h₂₃</span> <span class=\"fn\">⋯</span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Variant of `IsPushout.of_right` where `h₂₂` is induced from a morphism `h₂₃ : X₂₁ ⟶ X₂₃`, and\nthe universal property of the left square.\n\nThe objects in the statement fit into the following diagram:\n```\nX₁₁ - h₁₁ -> X₁₂ - h₁₂ -> X₁₃\n|            |            |\nv₁₁          v₁₂          v₁₃\n↓            ↓            ↓\nX₂₁ - h₂₁ -> X₂₂ - h₂₂ -> X₂₃\n```\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Limits/Shapes/Pullback/IsPullback/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.IsPushout.of_left'","kind":"theorem","line":569,"name":"CategoryTheory.IsPushout.of_left'","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Limits/Shapes/Pullback/IsPullback/Basic.lean#L569-L585"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Limits/Shapes/Pullback/IsPullback/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.IsPushout.of_top'\"><span class=\"name\">CategoryTheory</span>.<span class=\"name\">IsPushout</span>.<span class=\"name\">of_top'</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">C</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u₁}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Category\">Category.{v₁, u₁}</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">X₁₁ </span><span class=\"fn\">X₁₂ </span><span class=\"fn\">X₂₁ </span><span class=\"fn\">X₂₂ </span><span class=\"fn\">X₃₁ </span><span class=\"fn\">X₃₂</span> : <span class=\"fn\">C</span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">h₁₁</span> : <span class=\"fn\">X₁₁</span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Combinatorics/Quiver/Basic.html#Quiver.Hom\">⟶</a> <span class=\"fn\">X₁₂</span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">h₂₁</span> : <span class=\"fn\">X₂₁</span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Combinatorics/Quiver/Basic.html#Quiver.Hom\">⟶<